name: Jennie Hays
what_you_do: I'm Jennie Hays, a former paramedic with over 20 years of experience, now specializing in helping women entrepreneurs break through emotional and mindset blocks using brainspotting.
who_you_serve: I specialize in helping women entrepreneurs — especially those struggling with imposter syndrome, overwhelm, self-sabotage, and fear of being seen.
social_proof: I'm certified in brainspotting, hypnosis, and NLP, and I use methods inspired by Accelerated Resolution Therapy, Rapid Resolution Therapy, and Internal Family Systems.
